Trinity::
Looks down and thinks. "Well, let's see.  I was with Archangle at 
that one base.  Before that? I was in my pod.  There was a huge 
spider bot there(Tarantulus), and another bot(Koj).  That's all I can 
think of."  She looked up at him. Then she became wide eyed as she 
remembered another.  "There was one bot, someone called him, ah, 
hell..breath, I think." She shrugged her shoulders. "That's about 
it."
